Desert Scene Material Selection
Desert Scene

1. Selected Materials
- Wooden house: Western cartoon style, appropriate size
- Rocks: suitable for jumping obstacles, clear texture
- Sand terrain: seamless tiling, fits desert environment

2. Selection Criteria
- Match team cartoon low-poly style
- Low polygon count to avoid lag
- Importable into Unity
- Support collision and scripts

3. Usage Priority
1. Track & Terrain (Highest)
2. Wooden House & Rocks (High)
3. Bonfire & Decorations (Medium)
4. Effects & Audio (Low)